import React from 'react' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { LogOut, reset} from "../features/authSlice" const NavbarLogin = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const navigate = useNavigate() const {user} = useSelector((state) => state.auth) const logout = () => { dispatch(LogOut()) dispatch(reset()) navigate('/') } return (

Halo, {user && user.name} | Role : {user && user.role}

) } export default NavbarLogin
